Program: The Forum
Title: Cloud Education: The Future of Learning
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p02qm95w
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 11 May 2015
What are the big challenges in education around the World? How do we ensure everyone learns to the best of their ability? Is new technology the answer? And what does it mean for teachers and pupils? Exploring future learning, educational and creative leader Sir Ken Robinson, Professor of educational technology Sugata Mitra and Professor of cognitive science and computer science and engineering Scott Klemmer. Photo: equations and clouds (Photo/illustration by Shan Pillay) Show less